but I'm afraid you'll have
to work late this evening.

1172
01:26:28,615 --> 01:26:31,917
The dress needs to be ready
by 9:00 a.m.

1173
01:26:31,918 --> 01:26:34,519
to make its journey to Belgium.

1174
01:26:34,520 --> 01:26:38,323
Do expect to be here
for quite some time.

1175
01:26:38,324 --> 01:26:40,326
If you need to use
the telephone,

1176
01:26:40,327 --> 01:26:41,995
