Thank you.

1180
01:26:47,667 --> 01:26:49,602
CYRIL:
Ladies, I'm very sorry,

1181
01:26:49,603 --> 01:26:51,638
but I'm afraid you'll have
to work late this evening.

1182
01:26:51,639 --> 01:26:53,840
The dress needs to be ready
by 9:00 a.m.,

1183
01:26:53,841 --> 01:26:56,709
