1576
02:02:05,050 --> 02:02:09,053
<i>And I see a time near the end.</i>

1577
02:02:09,054 --> 02:02:13,456
<i>I can predict the future,
and everything has settled.</i>

1578
02:02:13,457 --> 02:02:16,727
