and I see things differently,</i>

1585
02:02:43,488 --> 02:02:46,662
<i>and I finally understand you.</i>

1586
02:02:51,662 --> 02:02:55,599
<i>And I take care of your dresses.</i>

1587
02:02:55,600 --> 02:02:58,469
